     <h3>ABOUT THE RESTAURANT SYSTEM</h3>
     <p>•  The Website or the system is open from 9 am to 9 pm</p>
     <p>•  The Unregistered customer is unable to make any transaction on the website, but they can view the website homepage.</p>
     <p>•  Upon creating an account on the website, the customer is asked to submit 3 pictures back-to-back pictures of their ID and them along with their ID this is to secure that there will be no scamming or using of other people’s identity.</p>
     <p>•  The user account is manually checked and verified by the admin /manager and it takes 2-5 mins on verifying their customer account.</p>
     <p>•  The customer can input their remarks or request and reminder if there are any ingredients that they would not like to include or they had allergies with that is in that particular dish. The request will also be submitted along with the orders and reservations that they make.</p>
     <p>•  When booking a reservation, the customer also needed to fill up a health declaration form that will be presented by the system, so that when they arrived at the restaurant their body temperature will only be taken.</p>

