     <h3>RESERVATION</h3>
     <p>•	To successfully make a reservation the customer will be asked to pay a down payment</p>
     <p>•	The table reservation fee will be based on the number of customers that will arrive. The minimum number of persons per table reservation is 1 person while the maximum is 15 persons. The reservation fee per 11 persons will be 70 pesos.</p>
     <p>•	GCash payment is the payment method that will be used by the customer to pay their reservation fee</p>
     <p>•	The customer will be reminded of their table reservation twice through text message by restaurant management. The first one is 15 mins before the reserved time of the customer and the second will be at the exact time of the reservation.</p>
     <p>•	The restaurant will give them 2-3 minutes allotted time to the customer, if the customer did not show on the given allotted time the reserved table will be canceled by the management and allow their walk-in customer to use that table.</p>
    
